Table.TblSQL: select `projects`.`name` AS `name`,`resource`.`name` AS `name1`,`dept`.`name` AS `name2`,`allocation`.`percentage` AS `percentage`,`allocation`.`allocation_from` AS `allocation_from`,`allocation`.`allocation_to` AS `allocation_to`,`resource`.`email` AS `email`,`allocation`.`Milestone` AS `Milestone`,`allocation`.`days` AS `days`,`allocation`.`deliverables` AS `deliverables`,`allocation`.`Location` AS `location`,`allocation`.`Task` AS `Task`,`allocation`.`shadow` AS `shadow` from (((`projects` join `allocation` on((`allocation`.`project_id` = `projects`.`name`))) join `resource` on((`allocation`.`resource_id` = `resource`.`email`))) join `dept` on((`dept`.`id` = `resource`.`dep`)))

select `projects`.`name` AS `name`,`resource`.`name` AS `name1`,`dept`.`name` AS `name2`,`allocation`.`Iteration Period` AS `Iteration Period`,`allocation`.`percentage` AS `percentage`,`allocation`.`allocation_from` AS `allocation_from`,`allocation`.`allocation_to` AS `allocation_to`,`resource`.`email` AS `email`,`allocation`.`cost` AS `cost`,`allocation`.`deliverables` AS `deliverables`,`allocation`.`days` AS `days`,`allocation`.`shadow` AS `shadow`,`allocation`.`Phase` AS `phase_name`,`milestone`.`Milestone` AS `Milestone1`,`allocation`.`Location` AS `Location`,`allocation`.`Task` AS `Task`,`allocation`.`project_id` AS `project_id` from ((((`projects` join `allocation` on((`allocation`.`project_id` = `projects`.`name`))) join `resource` on((`allocation`.`resource_id` = `resource`.`email`))) join `dept` on((`dept`.`id` = `resource`.`dep`))) join `milestone` on(((`allocation`.`Milestone` = `milestone`.`Milestone`) and (`allocation`.`project_id` = `milestone`.`projects_id`))))

select `projects`.`name` AS `name`,`resource`.`name` AS `name1`,`dept`.`name` AS `name2`,`allocation`.`percentage` AS `percentage`,`allocation`.`allocation_from` AS `allocation_from`,`allocation`.`allocation_to` AS `allocation_to`,`resource`.`email` AS `email`,`allocation`.`Milestone` AS `Milestone`,`allocation`.`days` AS `days`,`allocation`.`deliverables` AS `deliverables`,`allocation`.`Location` AS `location`,`allocation`.`Task` AS `Task`,`allocation`.`shadow` AS `shadow` from (((`projects` join `allocation` on((`allocation`.`project_id` = `projects`.`name`))) join `resource` on((`allocation`.`resource_id` = `resource`.`email`))) join `dept` on((`dept`.`id` = `resource`.`dep`))) where (ucase(`allocation`.`project_id`) in ('DEMO','PRESALES'))

select `allocation`.`Phase` AS `phase`,`cp`.`name` AS `CP Name`,`grade`.`GradeName` AS `Grade Name`,`projects`.`name` AS `Project Name`,`resource`.`name` AS `Resource Name`,`dept`.`name` AS `Product`,`allocation`.`percentage` AS `Percentage`,`allocation`.`allocation_from` AS `Date From`,`allocation`.`allocation_to` AS `Date To`,`allocation`.`Milestone` AS `Milestone`,`allocation`.`Iteration Period` AS `Iteration Period`,`allocation`.`days` AS `Duration`,`allocation`.`shadow` AS `Type`,concat('Q',quarter(`allocation`.`allocation_from`)) AS `quarters`,(select `grade2`.`mandayrate` from `grade2` where ((`grade2`.`dept` = `dept`.`name`) and (`grade2`.`quarter` = convert(`quarters` using latin1)) and (`grade2`.`year` = year(`allocation`.`allocation_from`)) and (`grade2`.`GradeName` = `grade`.`GradeName`))) AS `rate`,cast(((((`allocation`.`percentage` * `allocation`.`days`) * `allocation`.`shadow`) * (select `grade2`.`mandayrate` from `grade2` where ((`grade2`.`dept` = `dept`.`name`) and (`grade2`.`quarter` = convert(`quarters` using latin1)) and (`grade2`.`year` = year(`allocation`.`allocation_from`)) and (`grade2`.`GradeName` = `grade`.`GradeName`)))) / 100) as decimal(10,3)) AS `Cost` from (((((`projects` join `allocation` on((`allocation`.`project_id` = `projects`.`name`))) join `resource` on((`allocation`.`resource_id` = `resource`.`email`))) join `dept` on((`dept`.`id` = `resource`.`dep`))) join `grade`) join `cp`) where ((`cp`.`name` = `projects`.`CP`) and (`grade`.`id` = `resource`.`grade_id`)) order by `allocation`.`shadow`

select `phase`.`projects_id` AS `projects_id`,`phase`.`phase_name` AS `phase_name`,`phase`.`Budget` AS `Budget`,`phase`.`Planned_Cost` AS `planned_cost`,`phase`.`Revised_Plan` AS `revised_plan`,sum(`finance`.`Cost`) AS `SUM(finance.cost)`,(`phase`.`Budget` - sum(`finance`.`Cost`)) AS `NetProfit/Loss` from (`phase` join `finance`) where ((`finance`.`phase` = `phase`.`phase_name`) and (`finance`.`Project Name` = `phase`.`projects_id`)) group by `phase`.`projects_id`,`phase`.`phase_name`,`phase`.`Planned_Cost`,`phase`.`Revised_Plan`

select sql_cache `Employee_ALL_free_CONCAT_union`.`name` AS `name`,`Employee_ALL_free_CONCAT_union`.`Iteration Period` AS `Iteration Period`,`Employee_ALL_free_CONCAT_union`.`Allocation` AS `Allocation`,`Employee_ALL_free_CONCAT_union`.`Free` AS `Free`,`Employee_ALL_free_CONCAT_union`.`vacationcol` AS `vacationcol`,`Employee_ALL_free_CONCAT_union`.`product` AS `product`,`Employee_ALL_free_CONCAT_union`.`No of days` AS `No of days`,`Employee_ALL_free_CONCAT_union`.`Comments` AS `Comments` from `Employee_ALL_free_CONCAT_union`
